            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>(S.) In nomine Dei eterni amen. Anno eiusdem incarnacionis mill[esimo] C XX
                        quarto, indicione secunda, undecimo callendas iulii. In presencia <rs
                            key="#Boni_viri/boni_homines">bonorum hominum</rs> quorum nomina subter
                        leguntur, et est <persName
                            key="#Boni_viri/boni_homines #Commutatio #Promissio #Landed_possessions"
                            ref="#people/3575">Tiso</persName>, <persName
                            key="#Boni_viri/boni_homines #Commutatio #Promissio"><name ref="Berta"
                                >Berta</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Boni_viri/boni_homines #Commutatio #Promissio #siblingOf #Witness"
                            ref="#people/3565">Albericus</persName> de <placeName ref="#places/4106"
                            >Romano</placeName>, <persName
                            key="#Boni_viri/boni_homines #Commutatio #Promissio #siblingOf #Witness"
                            ref="#people/3566">Eceli</persName>
                        <rs key="#siblingOf">germani</rs>, <persName
                            key="#Boni_viri/boni_homines #Commutatio #Promissio #Witness"><name
                                ref="Ingelbertus">Ingelperto</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Boni_viri/boni_homines #Commutatio #Promissio #Witness"><name
                                ref="Berteradus">Berteraso</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Boni_viri/boni_homines #Commutatio #Promissio #Witness"><name
                                ref="Hugo">Ugo</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Boni_viri/boni_homines #Commutatio #Promissio #Witness"><name
                                ref="Cerro/de Smasaterra">Cerro</name></persName> de
                            <placeName>Smasaterra</placeName>, <persName
                            key="#Boni_viri/boni_homines #Commutatio #Promissio"><name
                                ref="Rodulfus">Rodulfo</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Boni_viri/boni_homines #Commutatio #Promissio"><name
                                ref="Heinricus/de Margano">Henrico</name></persName> de <placeName
                            ref="#places/4107">Margano</placeName> et reliqui plures. Ibique in
                        eorum presencia <persName key="#Abbots" ref="#people/3564">Uberto</persName>
                        <rs key="#Abbots">abas</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Abbots" ref="#juridical_persons/2419">Scanti
                            Floriani</orgName> acepit <rs key="#Commutatio">cambium</rs> a Tiso de
                        hoc quod predicta eclesia Scanti Floriani habebat in <placeName
                            ref="#places/4108">Camposion</placeName>, que est subdita <placeName
                            key="#Dioecesis #Mother_churches" ref="#places/41"
                            >Pataviensi</placeName>
                        <rs key="#Dioecesis #Mother_churches">epissco[pa]tu</rs>, secundum hoc quod
                        pactus fuit <persName key="#Bishops" ref="#people/3567"
                            >Sinebaldus</persName>
                        <rs key="#Bishops">episscopus</rs>, et permutacione fecerat cum eo et ipse
                        Uberto <rs key="#Advocatus">avocatore</rs> suo, vidilicet <rs key="#Price"
                            >quatuor libras Veronensis monete</rs> et <rs key="#Landed_possessions"
                            >terram</rs> quam sibi desigata est in <placeName
                            key="#Landed_possessions" ref="#places/4109">Marostica</placeName>.
                        Quidem predictus abas spondidit atque promisit <persName key="#Abbots"
                            ref="#people/3538">Poncio</persName> abati suisque sucesoribus una cum
                        suo avocatorei sucesores eius taciti et contenti permanere; quod si non
                        fecerit vel aliquo tempore molestaverit eos aut ullo ingenio ullaque
                        ocasione agere vel re causa presumserit, pena obligavit que est <rs
                            key="#Penalty">auri obtimi libras X argenti pondera XX</rs>; et quod re
                        quesierit vendicare non valeat, set presens permutacio inconcusam
                        perma[ne]at cum stipulacione subnixa. Actum in Camposion felliciter. ++++
                        manu predicti abati qui hac <rs key="#Promissio">cartulam promisionis</rs>
                        fieri rogavit et cambium accepi. +++ manu <persName
                            key="#Commutatio #Promissio #Witness" ref="#people/3577"
                            >Ianatas</persName>, Eceli, Alberici, Berteraso de Smasaterra, Ugo,
                        Cerro, Ingelperto rogati <rs key="#Witness">testes</rs>. Quidem ego
                            <persName key="#Commutatio #Promissio #Judge #Notary"><name
                                ref="Ardericus/iudex et noatrius">Ardericus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Judge">iudex</rs> et <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs> domini
                            <persName key="#Emperor/king" ref="#people/127">Henrici</persName>
                        quarto Romanorum <rs key="#Emperor/king">imperatore</rs> tardita complevi. </ab>
                </div>
